@page "/about"
@layout MainLayout

<div class="about-header">
    <h1 class="page-title">About Me</h1>
    <div class="title-underline"></div>
</div>

<div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-main">
        <p class="lead-text">
            I'm <strong>Cindy Amaquiton</strong>, 19, from Cortihan, Tapilon, Daanbantayan, Cebu.
        </p>
        
        <p class="body-text">
            Truth be told, IT wasn't my dream. Like many others, I found myself here not by choice but by circumstance. 
            Some days I question if I belong, other days I surprise myself by actually understanding the code. 
            It's a journey of small victories and constant doubts.
        </p>
        
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <p>"Not everyone has it all figured out. Some of us are still finding our way, and that's perfectly okay."</p>
        </div>
        
        <p class="body-text">
            Living in Cortihan means limited resources and unpredictable internet connection. 
            But growing up in a small coastal village taught me resilience. I find ways to submit projects, 
            study without constant guidance, and push through even when motivation runs low.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Currently Learning</h3>
            <ul class="skill-list">
                <li>C# & .NET Framework</li>
                <li>Web Development (HTML/CSS)</li>
                <li>Database Management (SQL)</li>
                <li>Blazor Basics</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Interests</h3>
            <ul class="interest-list">
                <li>UI/UX Design</li>
                <li>Frontend Development</li>
                <li>Digital Art</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>